          "n_students": 30800
        }
      ],
      "sample_filtering_criteria": "Used the full available PISA 2022 Spanish student sample (15-year-olds) with n = 30,800. The analytic dataset was constructed from 74 student contextual variables spanning socio-economic/cultural, psychological, cognitive/academic, and ICT domains, then preprocessed for data completeness/quality and reduced to 16 derived variables prior to k-means clustering. PISA test scores were not used for clustering, but academic performance differences across clusters were later examined."
    },
